<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM11.3">
<l>poṅkōtañ cūḻnta puvaṉiyum viṇṇulaku</l>
<l>maṅkātuñ cōrāmē yāḷkiṉṟa vemperumāṉ</l>
<l>ceṅkō luṭaiya tiruvaraṅkac celvaṉā</l>
<l>reṅkōl vaḷaiyā liṭartīrva rākātē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will our Lord—who rules over the earth surrounded by the raging seas</l>
<l>and the celestial world in such a way that nothing there comes to grief—,</l>
<l>the wealthy Man from Śrīraṅgam with the righteous sceptre</l>
<l>not end [His] trouble by means our kōl-bangles?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
